<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 15:13:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国土安全部称美国包机驱逐中国移民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-deported-chinese-migrants-charter-flight-homeland-security-says-2024-07-02/</link><description>美国国土安全部周二表示，美国在周末将试图非法入境的中国人驱逐回中国，这是自 2018 年以来的首次大型包机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:22:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-deported-chinese-migrants-charter-flight-homeland-security-says-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国将六家公司列入贸易限制名单，其中四家用于培训中国军队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-adds-six-companies-trade-restriction-list-four-training-chinas-military-2024-07-02/</link><description>据政府公告称，美国周二将六家公司列入贸易限制名单，其中四家因与中国军队训练有联系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:23:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-adds-six-companies-trade-restriction-list-four-training-chinas-military-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>文件显示，拜登2024年吊销了中国华为的8张许可证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-revoked-8-licenses-chinas-huawei-2024-document-shows-2024-07-02/</link><description>路透社看到的一份文件显示，拜登政府今年吊销了八项允许一些公司向中国电信设备巨头华为运送货物的许可证，试图向这家复兴的公司施压。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-revoked-8-licenses-chinas-huawei-2024-document-shows-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪与法国艾文斯建立欧洲合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-forms-european-partnership-with-frances-ayvens-2024-07-02/</link><description>法国兴业银行的汽车租赁部门艾文斯与中国电动汽车公司比亚迪周二宣布建立欧洲市场合作伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:01:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-forms-european-partnership-with-frances-ayvens-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，京东是英国包裹公司 Evri 的可能竞购者之一</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/jdcom-among-possible-bidders-british-parcel-company-evri-sources-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，中国在线零售商京东已成为探索潜在竞购英国包裹递送公司 Evri 的几家公司之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:49:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/jdcom-among-possible-bidders-british-parcel-company-evri-sources-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾将“坚持不懈”保护南海利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-be-relentless-protecting-interests-south-china-sea-2024-07-02/</link><description>菲律宾和中国周二一致认为，需要“恢复信任”和“重建信心”，以更好地管理海上争端，尽管马尼拉告诉其邻国，它将“毫不留情”地保护其在南海的利益。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-be-relentless-protecting-interests-south-china-sea-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>被控为中国从事间谍活动的挪威男子出庭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norwegian-citizen-arrested-alleged-spying-china-ntb-agency-reports-2024-07-02/</link><description>一名警方官员表示，一名挪威男子周二在奥斯陆法院出庭，面临代表中国从事间谍活动的指控，最初将被拘留四个星期，这是涉及中国在欧洲从事间谍活动的最新案件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:35:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norwegian-citizen-arrested-alleged-spying-china-ntb-agency-reports-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉 6 月中国制造电动汽车销量同比下降 24.2%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-june-china-made-ev-sales-down-242-yy-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周二的数据显示，特斯拉6月份中国制造的电动汽车销量同比下降24.2%至71,007辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-june-china-made-ev-sales-down-242-yy-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国和澳大利亚在太平洋影响力竞赛中捐赠建筑物和机场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-australia-donate-buildings-airstrips-pacific-influence-race-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国在瓦努阿图捐赠了一座总统大楼，澳大利亚和新西兰则在邻国所罗门群岛斥资 5500 万澳元落成机场，以争夺在太平洋岛屿地区的影响力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:58:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-australia-donate-buildings-airstrips-pacific-influence-race-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>律师称，外国法官之争损害了香港商法中心的吸引力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-commercial-law-hub-allure-damaged-by-foreign-judges-row-lawyers-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>一些律师和专家表示，中国统治的香港最高法院两名英国法官的辞职不仅引发了人们对法治的担忧，还将进一步削弱人们对香港更广泛的商业法律部门的信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 06:04:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-commercial-law-hub-allure-damaged-by-foreign-judges-row-lawyers-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪电动汽车季度销量增长 21%，缩小与特斯拉的差距</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-posts-21-jump-quarterly-ev-sales-closes-gap-with-tesla-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国比亚迪第二季度电动汽车销量增长 21%，在第一季度将全球最大电动汽车供应商头衔拱手让给美国竞争对手特斯拉后，缩小了与特斯拉的差距。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 05:06:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-posts-21-jump-quarterly-ev-sales-closes-gap-with-tesla-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>解说：中国计划制定的金融稳定法是什么？它将如何运作？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/what-is-chinas-planned-financial-stability-law-how-will-it-work-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国即将公布其金融稳定法，其中包括设立一个基金来救助陷入困境的金融机构，这是北京为防止世界第二大经济体发生系统性金融风险而采取的更广泛努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:57:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/what-is-chinas-planned-financial-stability-law-how-will-it-work-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>大型开发商销售降幅收窄后，中国房地产企业大幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-property-firms-jump-after-big-developers-show-smaller-sales-drop-2024-07-02/</link><description>私人数据显示，6 月份中国主要房地产开发商的销售额跌幅继续收窄，周二在香港上市的中国房地产公司股价大幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:29:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-property-firms-jump-after-big-developers-show-smaller-sales-drop-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>梵蒂冈呼吁和平解决包括南海争端在内的冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-june-17-south-china-sea-incident-most-aggressive-recent-chinese-2024-07-02/</link><description>梵蒂冈周二呼吁和平解决冲突，包括菲律宾和中国之间的紧张局势，因为两国正在努力解决南海争端。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-june-17-south-china-sea-incident-most-aggressive-recent-chinese-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>印尼协会称中国球员张因心脏骤停去世</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/chinese-player-zhang-died-cardiac-arrest-indonesia-association-says-2024-07-02/</link><description>印度尼西亚羽毛球协会（PBSI）表示，17岁的中国运动员张志杰在周日的一场比赛中倒地后因心脏骤停死亡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 03:26:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/chinese-player-zhang-died-cardiac-arrest-indonesia-association-says-2024-07-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>